---
// /underground/ghost — a hidden door. Unlinked from nav, noindex. The only way
// in is the Null Island coordinate (0,0) in the ticker. Diegetic GHOST voice;
// an honest payoff (Null Island is a real, symbolic place) plus a tease of the
// real-world Stationszeichen layer. See docs/Easter-Eggs-and-ARG-Spec.md.
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro'
---
<Base
  title="0,0 — DATAVISM"
  description="Null Island. Where the lost data surfaces."
  noindex
  chrome={false}
  footer={false}
>
  <main class="door">
    <div class="frame">
      <p class="coord font-mono">0.0000°N · 0.0000°E</p>
      <h1 class="font-display">NULL<br />ISLAND</h1>

      <p class="lede">No land here. It is the address every broken record defaults
        to — the point off the coast of Africa where mis-tagged, nulled and quietly
        manipulated data washes up when no one assigns it a place.</p>

      <p class="body">So that is where the Ghost keeps the interchange. All five
        lines converge on the data nobody meant to leave behind.</p>

      <p class="ghost font-mono">&gt; you followed a coordinate that points to nothing.<br />&gt; good. you already understand the method.</p>

      <div class="next">
        <span class="k font-mono">// NEXT STOP</span>
        <p>The next coordinates will not be null. Q4 2026 — three cities. The
          Stationszeichen surface in the streets: artefacts, not advertising.
          Watch the map. The Ghost is already sending.</p>
      </div>

      <a class="back font-mono" href="/">← back to the surface</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .door {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    padding: 60px 24px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(58% 42% at 50% 0%, rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.06), transparent 70%),
      var(--color-bg);
  }
  .frame { max-width: 56ch; }
  .coord {
    font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.28em; color: var(--color-ghost);
    margin: 0 0 18px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(48px, 12vw, 104px); line-height: 0.9; letter-spacing: -0.045em;
    color: var(--color-ink); margin: 0 0 28px;
  }
  .lede { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--color-ink-2); margin: 0 0 16px; }
  .body { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--color-ink-3); margin: 0 0 26px; }
  .ghost {
    font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.95; color: var(--color-ghost);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-ghost); padding-left: 16px; margin: 0 0 30px;
  }
  .next { border-top: 1px solid var(--color-edge); padding-top: 22px; margin-bottom: 34px; }
  .next .k { font-size: 10.5px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--color-ink-4); }
  .next p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--color-ink-3); margin: 10px 0 0; }
  .back { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--color-ink-4); text-decoration: none; }
  .back:hover { color: var(--color-ink); }
</style>
